; Coverage for amount.cc lines 204, 220:
; Standard US-style output with comma thousands separator and period decimal.
; Line 204: outputs '.' for decimal point when commodity has THOUSANDS style
;           but NOT decimal-comma or time-colon.
; Line 220: outputs ',' as thousands separator in the same context.

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

2024/01/01 Large payment
    Expenses:Rent          $12,345.67
    Assets:Cash

test bal
         $-12,345.67  Assets:Cash
          $12,345.67  Expenses:Rent
--------------------
                   0
end test
